  "excerpt": "<p>Yesterday I shared a photo from my trip to Longwood Gardens last week. Husband and I took the day off to make the trip and check out the Christmas light displays before they were gone. Plus, I try to do something special every year on what would be Mom’s birthday, so this was the perfect thing!</p>\n",
  "content": "<p><strong><a href=\"/wordless-wednesday/\">Yesterday</a></strong> I shared a photo from my trip to Longwood Gardens last week. Husband and I took the day off to make the trip and check out the Christmas light displays before they were gone. Plus, I try to do something special every year on what would be Mom’s birthday, so this was the perfect thing!</p>\n<p>We spent the whole day there, wandering around, grabbing lunch, listening to the organ play Christmas music and checking out all the lights once they were lit up! We walked around the entire grounds, stopping here or there to have some of the hot tea we packed to warm up. Later when it was dark, we walked the entire grounds again to see everything sparkly and bright. Here are a ton of photos from our long but wonderful day!</p>\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0114-1.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0112-2.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Risk taker Geese slowly skidded to the edge of the ice for a cold drink.</p>\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-7501-3.jpeg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0115-4.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0119-5.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0123-6.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0128-7.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0129-8.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0131-9.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0133-10.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0134-11.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0136-12.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0138-13.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0145-14.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0148-15.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0149-16.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0146-17.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0152-18.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0153-19.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0151-20.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0155-21.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0156-22.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<figure id=\"attachment_7519\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7519\" style=\"width: 1326px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7519 post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0157-23.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"980\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7519\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Later, you’ll see this all lit up!</figcaption></figure>\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0162-24.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0163-25.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7522 post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0164-26.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"980\"></p>\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0165-27.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0170-28.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0171-29.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">After a few hours outside in the cold, we were glad to reach the Conservatory! It meant we could spend a couple hours warmed up and look at pretty indoor displays! This is also where the organ room is, so we were able to listen to some beautiful Christmas music!</p>\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0175-30.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0173-31.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7528 post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0177-32.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"980\"></p>\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0178-33.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0179-34.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7531 post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0181-35.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"365\"></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7532 post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0182-36.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"980\"></p>\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0185-37.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0186-38.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7602 post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-1762-39.jpeg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"980\"></p>\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0188-40.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0190-41.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0200-42.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0201-43.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0204-44.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0203-45.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0205-46.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7604 post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-4279-47.jpeg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"746\" height=\"995\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Every nook had a differently colored and decorated tree. It was lovely!</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7542 post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0207-48.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"1307\"></p>\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0229-49.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0248-50.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0220-51.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0234-52.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7554 post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0246-53.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"735\"></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7543 post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0216-54.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"341\"></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7547 post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0228-55.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"1307\"></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7544 post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0217-56.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"735\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Here’s a little video of the fountain in the middle!</p>\n<div style=\"width: 980px;\" class=\"wp-video\">\n<video class=\"wp-video-shortcode\" id=\"video-7494-1\" width=\"980\" height=\"551\" preload=\"metadata\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"video/mp4\" src=\"http://www.katiecrafts.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/IMG_0225.m4v?_=1\" ><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/IMG_0225.m4v\">http://www.katiecrafts.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/IMG_0225.m4v</a></video></div>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7552 post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0241-57.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"735\"></p>\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0249-58.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0250-59.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0235-60.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0256-61.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Love the orchid room!</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7558 post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0253-62.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"422\"></p>\n<p>Different grades from schools in the area were able to decorate a room full of trees using a blue and white theme! They were really adorable!! Here are all the trees I saw, and a couple close ups of handmade ornaments too!</p>\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0271-63.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0273-64.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0259-65.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0260-66.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0261-67.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0262-68.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0263-69.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0264-70.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0265-71.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0267-72.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0268-73.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0269-74.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0270-75.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0272-76.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0274-77.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0276-78.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0280-79.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0294-80.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">How pretty are these spray roses?!</p>\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0286-81.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0285-82.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Many plants and trees had glass and crystal ornaments that looked like icicles. So classy!</p>\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0288-83.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0290-84.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7583 post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0296-85.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"980\"></p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7584\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7584\" style=\"width: 1326px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7584 post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0302-86.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"980\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7584\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Husband made friends with another Longwood Kitty!</figcaption></figure>\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0308-87.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0306-88.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7587 post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0309-89.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"735\"></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7588 post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0311-90.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"980\"></p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7589\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7589\" style=\"width: 1326px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7589 post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0318-91.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"980\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7589\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Here’s the tree in the Italian gardens, all lit up!</figcaption></figure>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7593 post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0322-92.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"1307\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">This tree by the lake was decorated by the staff. It’s ornaments are made from items found on the property!</p>\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0319-93.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0320-94.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0321-95.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7594 post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0324-96.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"980\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">We loved the fire pit made out of an old steel drum. Check out a video of the flames licking the sides below!</p>\n<div style=\"width: 640px;\" class=\"wp-video\"><video class=\"wp-video-shortcode\" id=\"video-7494-2\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" preload=\"metadata\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"video/mp4\" src=\"http://www.katiecrafts.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/IMG_0326.m4v?_=2\" ><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/IMG_0326.m4v\">http://www.katiecrafts.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/IMG_0326.m4v</a></video></div>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7596\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7596\" style=\"width: 1326px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7596 post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0327-97.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"735\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7596\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Husband posing with the scary solitary red lit tree in the background!</figcaption></figure>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7597 post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0334-98.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"980\"></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7599 post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0339-99.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"242\"></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7598 post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0337-100.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"980\"></p>\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0340-101.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/a-longwood-christmas/img-0347-102.jpg\" alt=\"A Longwood Christmas on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p>Well, that’s my day/night at Longwood Gardens! I hope you enjoyed all my photos from our wonderful trip. Now that I have checked it out in the Summer and the Winter, I want to also see it in the Spring and Fall! Stay tuned for future visits. 🙂</p>\n<p>Which photo from my Longwood Gardens Christmas visit was your favorite?</p>\n",
